Terrorsaur:




Terrorsaur glanced at Dark Mouse strangely. He never thought a 
Predacon would greet another like that. 

"Why are the Predacons broken up? Where is everyone?"

"This guy's been spyin' on Megatron," Quickstrike cut 
in. "Talkin' 'bout clones and uh base in th' arctic." He blinked his 
glowing crimson optics at him. "Said he took Inferno, so he 
followed." 

The flier nodded his head. "Megatron left me behind, so I made my way 
back here. What's been going on?"

The Fuzor turned his head to Dark Mouse. "Wanna fill him in on that?"
